00:42:58,052 --> 00:43:01,249
Brian Keogh,
light heavyweight.

444
00:43:01,322 --> 00:43:05,383
Died 1973.
Age, 16 years.

445
00:43:05,459 --> 00:43:08,656
John Maguire, featherweight.

446
00:43:08,729 --> 00:43:12,597
Died 1983.
Age, 19 years.

447
00:43:12,667 --> 00:43:16,433
Tony Walsh, bantamweight.

448
00:43:16,504 --> 00:43:19,769
Died 1990.
Age, 20 years.

449
00:43:19,840 --> 00:43:24,277
Harry McCormack, flyweight.

450
00:43:24,345 --> 00:43:28,873
