Age, 13 years.

451
00:43:29,951 --> 00:43:31,441
Sammy Orr,

452
00:43:33,321 --> 00:43:35,380
lightweight.

453
00:43:35,456 --> 00:43:39,290
Died 1986.
Age, 22 years.

454
00:43:39,360 --> 00:43:44,491
Sammy's parents are Protestants
from East Belfast,

455
00:43:44,565 --> 00:43:46,863
and this is their first night
in the club...

456
00:43:46,934 --> 00:43:50,233
since the Troubles began
28 years ago.

457
00:43:52,373 --> 00:43:56,901
And I'd like you all
to welcome them back.

458
00:43:56,978 --> 00:44:01,210
[ Applause ]

459
00:44:07,088 --> 00:44:10,057
- Did you know that was gonna happen ?
- No.

460
00:44:10,124 --> 00:44:12,058
Sentimental shite.

461
00:44:12,126 --> 00:44:14,560
- [ Announcer ] Round one.
- [ Bell Dings, Cheering ]

