Keep your balance now.

463
00:44:21,035 --> 00:44:23,799
[ Man ]
Hit him ! Hit him !

464
00:44:23,871 --> 00:44:25,634
[ Man ]
Come on, Danny !

465
00:44:25,706 --> 00:44:28,732
