477
00:45:21,820 --> 00:45:23,981
[ Man ]
Stay off the ropes !

478
00:45:25,557 --> 00:45:28,458
That a boy, Danny !
Go on !

479
00:45:30,195 --> 00:45:32,356
- [ Grunts ]
- [ Crowd Gasps ]

480
00:45:32,430 --> 00:45:37,493
