482
00:45:40,705 --> 00:45:43,503
- [ Man ] Come on ! Get up !
- seven, eight--

483
00:45:43,575 --> 00:45:45,509
Box !

484
00:45:50,081 --> 00:45:52,106
- Break ! Break !
