01:05:30,592 --> 01:05:34,585
♪ And down the mountainside ♪

724
01:05:34,663 --> 01:05:37,723
♪ The summer's gone ♪

725
01:05:37,799 --> 01:05:42,133
♪ And all the flowers
are dying ♪

726
01:05:42,204 --> 01:05:46,140
Did you hear that ?
That'll put pride in your heart.

727
01:05:46,208 --> 01:05:50,201
Frank Patterson's out front. He runs the
Commonwealth Sporting Club in London.

728
01:05:50,278 --> 01:05:53,111
- He's got a big promotion comin' up.
- Not now, Matt.

729
01:05:53,181 --> 01:05:55,172
It's on television.

730
01:05:55,250 --> 01:05:57,514
lt's a fuckin' meat trade,
and we don't want it.

731
01:05:57,586 --> 01:05:59,520
There's a good
few grand in it.

732
01:05:59,588 --> 01:06:02,056
Forget about London.
Just concentrate on this fight.

733
01:06:02,124 --> 01:06:04,422
All right.
Time to go.

734
01:06:04,493 --> 01:06:08,452
No dressin' gown.
No nothin'.

735
01:06:08,530 --> 01:06:12,159
♪ But come ye back ♪

736
01:06:12,234 --> 01:06:16,568
♪ When summer's
in the meadow ♪

737
01:06:17,706 --> 01:06:22,109
♪ Or when the valley's hushed ♪

738
01:06:22,177 --> 01:06:24,407
♪ And white with snow ♪

739
01:06:24,479 --> 01:06:26,970
[ Cheering ]

740
01:06:27,049 --> 01:06:30,416
♪ 'Tis I'll be there ♪

741
01:06:30,485 --> 01:06:34,717
♪ ln sunshine or in shadow ♪

742
01:06:34,790 --> 01:06:37,520
[ Cheering Continues ]

743
01:06:37,592 --> 01:06:41,187
♪ Oh, Danny boy
Oh, Danny boy ♪

744
01:06:41,263 --> 01:06:44,426
♪ I love you so ♪♪

745
01:06:44,499 --> 01:06:47,093
[ Whistling, Cheering ]

746
01:06:47,169 --> 01:06:49,865
Okay, boys, let's go.
Follow my instructions.

747
01:06:49,938 --> 01:06:52,532
Protect yourselves,
and shake hands.

748
01:06:58,113 --> 01:07:00,673
[ Bell Dings ]

749
01:07:29,321 --> 01:07:31,983
Stop !
Go to a neutral corner.

750
01:07:32,057 --> 01:07:37,359
[ Referee ]
One ! Two ! Three ! Four !

751
01:07:37,429 --> 01:07:39,659
Five ! Six !

752
01:07:39,732 --> 01:07:41,996
Seven !
Are you all right ?

753
01:07:42,067 --> 01:07:44,661
- [ Crowd Shouting ]
- Box !

754
01:07:54,413 --> 01:07:57,075
Come on, Danny !

755
01:08:07,593 --> 01:08:11,154
[ Cheering ]

756
01:08:11,230 --> 01:08:14,097
[ Referee ]
One, two, three,

757
01:08:14,166 --> 01:08:17,863
four, five, six,

758
01:08:17,936 --> 01:08:19,870
seven, eight--

759
01:08:19,938 --> 01:08:22,429
- You okay ?
- I'm all right.

760
01:08:24,943 --> 01:08:26,877
[ Referee ]
Box !

761
01:08:31,683 --> 01:08:33,810
One, two, three,

762
01:08:33,886 --> 01:08:37,822
four, five, six, seven,

763
01:08:37,890 --> 01:08:40,757
eight, nine, ten !

764
01:08:40,826 --> 01:08:43,920
- [ Bell Dings ]
- [ Referee ] You're out !

765
01:08:43,996 --> 01:08:46,556
[ Crowd Whistling, Cheering ]

766
01:08:50,836 --> 01:08:53,498
Thanks very much.
Well done.

767
01:08:53,572 --> 01:08:55,733
Great night
for the city of Belfast.

768
01:08:55,808 --> 01:08:58,003
The crowd will be comin' out now,
Catholics and Protestants together.

769
01:08:58,076 --> 01:09:00,010
The band will lead them
off down the street.

770
01:09:00,078 --> 01:09:02,012
I'd like you to get as many
good pictures as you can.

771
01:09:02,080 --> 01:09:05,481
- Yea !
- Danny ! Danny ! Danny !

772
01:09:05,551 --> 01:09:11,251
They'll be coming out together, so
you can clear the barriers away. Okay.

773
01:09:11,323 --> 01:09:15,020
[ Chanting Continues ]
Danny ! Danny ! Danny !

774
01:09:16,595 --> 01:09:21,532
[ Chanting, Whistling,
Cheering Continue ]

775
01:09:24,703 --> 01:09:28,161
[ Explosion Resounding ]

776
01:09:28,240 --> 01:09:30,640
[ Chanting Stops,
Crowd Murmuring ]

777
01:09:36,915 --> 01:09:39,816
[ Crowd Murmuring ]

778
01:09:39,885 --> 01:09:44,879
Keep calm. You can all
see where your exits are.

779
01:09:44,957 --> 01:09:49,155
[ Matt ]
Don't panic. Get up slowly.

780
01:09:49,228 --> 01:09:51,992
Leave the building.

781
01:09:52,064 --> 01:09:54,965
Ju-- Just keep calm.

782
01:09:55,033 --> 01:09:58,992
There's absolutely
no need to panic.

783
01:09:59,071 --> 01:10:02,529
Go out through the main exit.

784
01:10:02,608 --> 01:10:05,133
They've killed the policeman,
Reggie Bell. Let's move.

785
01:10:05,210 --> 01:10:08,145
Jesus ! Come on.
Let's move it. Move it !

786
01:10:08,213 --> 01:10:11,011
[ Matt ] Follow
the exit signs behind you.

787
01:10:11,083 --> 01:10:16,043
[ Joe ] McCormack ! McCormack !
I wanna talk to you now !

788
01:10:16,121 --> 01:10:18,248
Go out through
the main exit.

789
01:10:18,323 --> 01:10:20,382
- Cop killer !
- There's no need to panic.

790
01:10:20,459 --> 01:10:23,394
- Catholic bastards ! Bastards !
- Follow the exit signs.

791
01:10:23,462 --> 01:10:25,259
You're all right, son.

792
01:10:25,330 --> 01:10:28,265
- Kill him ! Kill him !
- They killed a cop !

793
01:10:28,333 --> 01:10:30,893
You're okay.
Take his hand now, son.

794
01:10:30,969 --> 01:10:32,436
Keep calm.

795
01:10:32,504 --> 01:10:34,836
Watch yourself now.
That's right.

796
01:10:34,907 --> 01:10:37,501
- Good, lad.
- Oh, Daddy ! Oh, Daddy, no !

797
01:10:37,576 --> 01:10:38,838
- You'll be okay !
- Daddy !

798
01:10:38,911 --> 01:10:41,106
- Quit pushin' !
- Dad !

799
01:10:41,179 --> 01:10:43,739
Robert ! Robert !

800
01:10:43,815 --> 01:10:46,079
There's a kid
dyin' in there !

801
01:10:46,151 --> 01:10:49,609
Give him some space !
There's a kid dyin' in there !

802
01:10:53,825 --> 01:10:57,192
[ Shouting ]

803
01:10:57,262 --> 01:11:00,129
- [ Shouts ]
- Stop it ! Stop it !

804
01:11:05,270 --> 01:11:06,737
Irish pigs !

805
01:11:08,040 --> 01:11:09,974
[ Man Shouts ]

806
01:11:11,310 --> 01:11:12,868
Gary !

807
01:11:19,818 --> 01:11:22,582
[ Woman Screams ]

808
01:11:30,362 --> 01:11:32,956
[ Man ]
Oh ! Oh !

809
01:11:33,031 --> 01:11:34,589
- Aaah !
- [ Woman Screams ]

810
01:11:38,303 --> 01:11:42,899
- Run, Ned ! Run !
- Come on ! Run, will ya ?

811
01:11:43,976 --> 01:11:45,807
[ Shouting ]

812
01:11:45,877 --> 01:11:50,837
Where the fuck were you ?
What are these for ?

813
01:11:50,916 --> 01:11:53,077
They're the keys
to the gym. Come on.

814
01:11:53,151 --> 01:11:55,847
Where's the petrol ?

815
01:11:56,922 --> 01:11:59,857
[ Helicopter Whirring ]

816
01:12:01,927 --> 01:12:06,227
Should never have taken
that gear from him.

817
01:12:09,868 --> 01:12:11,802
Don't even think
about it, lke.

818
01:12:11,870 --> 01:12:15,829
He's a wife and
three children, Danny.

819
01:12:15,907 --> 01:12:19,399
Anything that
belongs to the cops.

820
01:12:19,478 --> 01:12:22,345
We'll burn it outside.

821
01:12:27,586 --> 01:12:30,817
- I'm not takin' that outside.
- Why not ?

822
01:12:30,889 --> 01:12:33,824
[ Mickey ] 'Cause, Liam,
the Brits are everywhere.

823
01:12:38,664 --> 01:12:40,689
We'll burn it here.

824
01:12:48,940 --> 01:12:51,408
Stop messin', Ned.

825
01:12:53,111 --> 01:12:54,544
- Aaah !
- Mickey !

826
01:12:54,613 --> 01:12:57,377
- Mickey !
- Aaah !

827
01:12:57,449 --> 01:12:59,508
Mickey, roll over !
Oh, geez !

828
01:12:59,584 --> 01:13:02,052
- Get him !
- Mickey, get up !

829
01:13:02,120 --> 01:13:04,350
- Aaah !
- [ Fire Alarm Ringing ]

830
01:13:04,423 --> 01:13:09,383
Gotta get outta here !
Let's get out ! Come on !

831
01:13:09,461 --> 01:13:12,430
- Let's get out !
- Run, Mickey ! Get out !

832
01:13:12,497 --> 01:13:15,193
The gym is on fire !

833
01:13:15,267 --> 01:13:19,704
- The gym's on fire !
- The gym's on fire !

834
01:13:19,771 --> 01:13:22,137
[ Man ]
The gym's on fire !

835
01:13:27,345 --> 01:13:31,281
[ Sirens Wailing ]

836
01:13:33,919 --> 01:13:37,116
[ Shouts ]

837
01:13:37,189 --> 01:13:42,388
- [ Fire Alarm Ringing ]
- [ Coughing ] Oh !

838
01:13:42,461 --> 01:13:47,728
[ Man On Megaphone ]
Get away from the building !

839
01:13:49,468 --> 01:13:50,799
Get the pictures !

840
01:13:50,869 --> 01:13:54,168
[ Man On Megaphone ]
This is for your own safety !

841
01:13:57,209 --> 01:14:00,576
- You'd better leave right now !
- Come on, lke !

842
01:14:00,645 --> 01:14:02,875
Time to get out !

843
01:14:08,453 --> 01:14:11,422
- You can't go in there !
- I work in there !

844
01:14:11,490 --> 01:14:13,822
- Step back !
- I work in there, and l have to get--

845
01:14:13,892 --> 01:14:15,826
It's not safe !

846
01:14:19,297 --> 01:14:20,992
Get away from the building !

847
01:14:21,066 --> 01:14:24,900
Serves youse bloody well right
for takin' the stuff from the police !

848
01:14:55,827 --> 01:14:58,591
I'm in the middle
of negotiations,

849
01:14:58,664 --> 01:15:02,395
and you let off
this fuckin' bomb.

850
01:15:02,467 --> 01:15:05,698
- What did you achieve by it ?
You achieved zero.
- Zero ?

851
01:15:05,771 --> 01:15:11,641
Grow up. Stop livin' in the past
and get your head into the future.

852
01:15:11,710 --> 01:15:16,044
You can keep goin'.
You can split this organization in two.

853
01:15:16,114 --> 01:15:19,743
- But you're gonna have
to accept the consequences.
- What consequences ?

854
01:15:19,818 --> 01:15:22,252
You know what
fuckin' consequences.

855
01:15:23,588 --> 01:15:26,989
You don't have
all the guns, Joe.

856
01:15:27,059 --> 01:15:32,156
A lot of the active servicemen won't
accept this peace bullshit anymore.

857
01:15:32,230 --> 01:15:34,164
Are you threatenin' me ?

858
01:15:34,232 --> 01:15:36,359
You're goin' soft, Joe.

859
01:15:36,435 --> 01:15:38,699
Ya think so ?

860
01:15:38,770 --> 01:15:41,568
You had men in prison...

861
01:15:41,640 --> 01:15:45,303
who starved themselves
to death for you, Joe.

862
01:15:45,377 --> 01:15:48,005
Ten of them.
Now you have Danny Boy Flynn...

863
01:15:48,080 --> 01:15:51,345
wanderin' around the place makin'
a mockery of everything you stood for,

864
01:15:51,416 --> 01:15:54,283
and you don't even see it.

865
01:15:54,353 --> 01:15:56,548
But a child can see it, Joe.

866
01:15:56,621 --> 01:15:58,714
A wee innocent child
can see the truth.

867
01:15:58,790 --> 01:16:01,657
What are you talkin' about ?

868
01:16:01,727 --> 01:16:05,026
Why don't you ask Liam
why he burnt down the gym ?

869
01:16:17,142 --> 01:16:19,076
I just follow orders.

870
01:16:21,446 --> 01:16:24,347
He's way out
of control, Joe.

871
01:16:24,416 --> 01:16:27,544
- [ Door Opens ]
- [ Man ] Hello, Maggie.

872
01:16:27,619 --> 01:16:29,553
- [ Door Closes ]
- [ Maggie ] Hi.

873
01:16:29,621 --> 01:16:32,112
- lt's your da.
- All right.

874
01:16:32,190 --> 01:16:34,124
Joe.

875
01:16:46,571 --> 01:16:49,062
What's wrong ?

876
01:16:49,141 --> 01:16:52,633
I don't want to lose you.

877
01:16:52,711 --> 01:16:55,646
Sure you never will.

878
01:16:55,714 --> 01:16:58,239
You've got to be
above reproach.

879
01:17:04,890 --> 01:17:09,350
Tell me-- Tell me
you don't love Danny Flynn.

880
01:17:14,399 --> 01:17:16,424
You've got to get rid of him.

881
01:17:23,375 --> 01:17:25,605
What are you
talkin' about ?

882
01:17:33,351 --> 01:17:35,785
- We've done nothin' wrong.
- That's not the point.

883
01:17:35,854 --> 01:17:39,051
- Everybody thinks you did.
- Well, to hell with them.

884
01:17:39,124 --> 01:17:41,285
To hell with 'em.

885
01:17:41,359 --> 01:17:47,195
Maggie, Liam burned down
the gym.

886
01:17:49,835 --> 01:17:51,769
Liam ?

887
01:18:01,847 --> 01:18:04,338
- Where is he ?
- Upstairs.

888
01:18:04,416 --> 01:18:06,884
[ Footsteps Approaching ]

889
01:18:13,258 --> 01:18:16,250
What the hell did you
think you were doing ?

890
01:18:16,328 --> 01:18:20,697
I saw ya.
I saw ya with him.

891
01:18:23,502 --> 01:18:27,666
You're gonna run away
with him, aren't ya ?

892
01:18:33,011 --> 01:18:35,639
No.

893
01:18:35,714 --> 01:18:39,514
I'm gonna stay
right here with you.

894
01:18:39,584 --> 01:18:42,280
I don't want to
see him ever again.

895
01:18:44,656 --> 01:18:46,681
Oh, Liam.

896
01:18:46,758 --> 01:18:49,226
- [ Footsteps Approaching ]
- Liam ?

897
01:18:56,635 --> 01:19:00,662
- [ Door Closes ]
- Leave him, Maggie.

898
01:19:00,739 --> 01:19:02,832
He's suffered enough.

899
01:19:10,415 --> 01:19:13,350
He's suffered enough ?

900
01:19:14,419 --> 01:19:16,353
Jesus.

901
01:19:20,091 --> 01:19:25,290
My marriage was over
before Liam was even born.

902
01:19:31,770 --> 01:19:33,738
I'm the prisoner here.

903
01:19:33,805 --> 01:19:38,003
You and your politics
have made sure of that.

904
01:19:38,076 --> 01:19:40,601
All l wanted was for you
to have a good marriage.

905
01:19:40,679 --> 01:19:45,048
- [ Scoffs ] Like you and my mother ?
- Yes.

906
01:19:45,116 --> 01:19:47,550
Do you know how much
it cost her to smile...

907
01:19:47,619 --> 01:19:50,315
every time you walked
through the front door ?

908
01:19:50,388 --> 01:19:54,119
She lived her whole bloody life
worried to death. And for what ?

909
01:19:56,194 --> 01:20:00,358
Will ya look me in the eye
and tell me for what ?

910
01:20:01,933 --> 01:20:04,868
I suppose she
believed in me, Maggie.

911
01:20:06,571 --> 01:20:10,268
She thought the ground
that you walked on was sacred.

912
01:20:10,342 --> 01:20:13,277
So did I.

913
01:20:14,813 --> 01:20:17,043
I'm not going to lose Danny.

914
01:20:17,115 --> 01:20:19,549
Then you'll have
to tell him to go.

915
01:20:19,618 --> 01:20:21,552
Why ?

916
01:20:21,620 --> 01:20:24,783
I can't protect him, Maggie.

917
01:20:27,158 --> 01:20:32,095
You'll have to get rid of him,
or you'll find him in a pool of blood.

918
01:20:34,532 --> 01:20:36,466
God help you.

919
01:20:45,577 --> 01:20:48,876
God help you, Father.

920
01:20:48,947 --> 01:20:51,108
[ Door Closes ]

921
01:20:51,249 --> 01:20:53,342
[ Knocking ]

922
01:20:56,421 --> 01:20:59,219
Maggie, come in.

923
01:21:03,561 --> 01:21:06,121
I have to talk to you, Danny.

924
01:21:06,197 --> 01:21:09,030
- Want a cup of tea ?
- Aye.

925
01:21:14,072 --> 01:21:16,006
[ Flame lgnites ]

926
01:21:25,483 --> 01:21:30,420
Danny, l-- l have something
to say to you.

927
01:21:33,458 --> 01:21:37,224
I've been up all night,
and I--

928
01:21:37,295 --> 01:21:39,286
I've written ya a letter.

929
01:21:39,364 --> 01:21:43,232
[ Paper Rustling ]

930
01:21:48,106 --> 01:21:50,199
''Dear Danny,

931
01:21:50,275 --> 01:21:54,211
''It's taken me 14 years
to learn to live without you,

932
01:21:54,279 --> 01:21:59,512
''and I don't believe that here
in this place you can ever be mine.

933
01:21:59,584 --> 01:22:04,214
''It's not possible because
too many people are gonna get hurt.

934
01:22:07,525 --> 01:22:09,493
''I have to protect
those I love.

935
01:22:09,561 --> 01:22:14,521
''I'm so sorry, Danny.
God bless you.

936
01:22:14,599 --> 01:22:17,659
Yours always, Maggie.''

937
01:22:46,196 --> 01:22:48,289
What do you want ?

938
01:22:48,365 --> 01:22:50,993
I'm askin' you to walk away.

939
01:22:53,269 --> 01:22:55,203
I don't think so.

940
01:22:55,271 --> 01:22:59,332
- You made a promise.
- What was that ?

941
01:22:59,409 --> 01:23:02,344
You said if I asked you
to leave, you'd leave.

942
01:23:02,412 --> 01:23:06,849
- Mmm, aye.
- Well, I'm askin'.

943
01:23:11,354 --> 01:23:13,379
Have you been threatened ?

944
01:23:13,456 --> 01:23:15,481
- Why do you say that ?
- Have you ?

945
01:23:15,558 --> 01:23:18,925
I do have a mind
of my own, Danny.

946
01:23:22,966 --> 01:23:27,903
I know I might very well be losin' it,
but I do have a mind of my own.

947
01:23:27,971 --> 01:23:31,031
Is it your father ?
Is it Joe ?

948
01:23:31,107 --> 01:23:33,871
No, Danny.

949
01:23:36,146 --> 01:23:38,080
It's Harry, isn't it ?

950
01:23:40,617 --> 01:23:42,209
Is it Harry ?

951
01:23:44,087 --> 01:23:47,545
Tell me.
Just fuckin' tell me.

952
01:23:47,624 --> 01:23:49,854
Don't, Danny.

953
01:23:52,529 --> 01:23:54,929
You don't understand.

954
01:23:54,998 --> 01:23:58,764
Half my fuckin' life I pissed away
and all the good things in it...

955
01:23:58,835 --> 01:24:01,963
because of that sickly bastard
and his dirty little,

956
01:24:02,038 --> 01:24:06,372
cozy little, fuckin' secret world
and all the dirt in it.

957
01:24:06,443 --> 01:24:11,540
And now he's tryin' to turn us into
a dirty little secret. So, fuck him !

958
01:24:13,783 --> 01:24:17,412
Let him know that
I love you, Maggie.

959
01:24:17,487 --> 01:24:20,422
Go out and tell him now.
Go and fuckin' tell him.

960
01:24:20,490 --> 01:24:24,824
I'll not crawl around in
the fuckin' gutter for him !

961
01:24:24,894 --> 01:24:27,761
I'll kill him first.
I'll rip his fuckin' throat out !

962
01:24:27,831 --> 01:24:30,061
Don't go outside.
That's what he wants you to do.

963
01:24:30,133 --> 01:24:32,601
That's what he wants me to do,
and I'll fuckin' do it !

964
01:24:32,669 --> 01:24:35,103
Liam burnt down the gym.

965
01:24:40,210 --> 01:24:44,510
- He saw us together.
- What are you talkin' about ?

966
01:24:47,083 --> 01:24:49,950
He thinks you're gonna
take me away from him.

967
01:25:08,571 --> 01:25:10,505
